{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020/04/baseliner-6-is-out/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"J. Pedro Ribeiro"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9e10046f-748e-5434-841c-83ee7017e8bf","excerpt":"Baseliner, my very own Chrome Extension has finally been published. An extension for designers and developers who care about grid alignment Born in 201â€¦","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 440px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8a51a834c969371face9ce096d53ddb6/48c0e/promo-440.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.92405063291139%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Baseliner logo\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8a51a834c969371face9ce096d53ddb6/48c0e/promo-440.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8a51a834c969371face9ce096d53ddb6/c26ae/promo-440.png 158w,\n/static/8a51a834c969371face9ce096d53ddb6/6bdcf/promo-440.png 315w,\n/static/8a51a834c969371face9ce096d53ddb6/48c0e/promo-440.png 440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/baseliner/agoopbiflnjadjfbhimhlmcbgmdgldld?hl=en-GB\">Baseliner</a>, my very own Chrome Extension has finally been published.</p>\n<h2>An extension for designers and developers who care about grid alignment</h2>\n<p>Born in 2015, <strong>Baseliner</strong> is a Chrome (and <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-GB/firefox/addon/baseliner-add-on/\">Firefox</a>) extension used by more than <strong>6.000</strong> users worldwide.</p>\n<p>The extension overlays a grid on top of any page, helping UX Designers &#x26; Developers build interfaces with pixel perfect metrics.</p>\n<h2>Version 6.0</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cd92e7eaaa1082c1cb8712b24a2749fc/f09ab/screenshot.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Baseliner logo\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/cd92e7eaaa1082c1cb8712b24a2749fc/f058b/screenshot.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cd92e7eaaa1082c1cb8712b24a2749fc/c26ae/screenshot.png 158w,\n/static/cd92e7eaaa1082c1cb8712b24a2749fc/6bdcf/screenshot.png 315w,\n/static/cd92e7eaaa1082c1cb8712b24a2749fc/f058b/screenshot.png 630w,\n/static/cd92e7eaaa1082c1cb8712b24a2749fc/40601/screenshot.png 945w,\n/static/cd92e7eaaa1082c1cb8712b24a2749fc/f09ab/screenshot.png 1250w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The newly deployed version 6.0 was completely built from scratch, based on the feedback I've received over the years.</p>\n<p><strong>Baseliner</strong> now enables both horizontal <strong>and</strong> vertical grid, by far the most requested feature.</p>\n<p>The extension is also faster and more performant thanks to the use of more modern tooling like React.js.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/baseliner/agoopbiflnjadjfbhimhlmcbgmdgldld?hl=en-GB\">Download Baseliner 6.0 on Chrome Web Store</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-GB/firefox/addon/baseliner-add-on/\">Download Baseliner 6.0 for Firefox</a></p>\n<h2>Feedback, bugs, suggestions, support</h2>\n<p>The project is on <a href=\"https://github.com/jpedroribeiro/Baseliner\">GitHub</a> and we welcome any suggestions that will help us improve this tool.\nFound any bug? Feel free to file an <a href=\"https://github.com/jpedroribeiro/Baseliner/issues/new/choose\">issue</a>.\nLike the extension? You can <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/jpedroribeiro\">buy us a coffee</a> and help maintain this project.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Baseliner 6.0 is out!","date":"April 18, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020/04/baseliner-6-is-out/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/01/nested-property-dot-notation/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Getting a nested property of an object with dot notation","tags":["nested properties","dot notation","javascript"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/05/book-notes-5-the-remarkable-life-of-the-skin/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Book Notes #5: The Remarkable Life of the Skin","tags":["book notes","skin","health"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454","792910177"],"slicesMap":{}}